PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1991-1798 of September 20, 1991, which authorized the sale to SOUTHPORT AEROSPACE CENTRE INC. of the land and infrastructure situated at the military base in Portage la Prairie, Manitoba, in order to remove a condition that calls for a right of first refusal in favour of Her Majesty if ever the property was sold to a third party and to replace the description of land involved.
